@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v1 - wp.sin(v2 + 0.81)) + ((v1 + 0.62 / v0 + 0.72) / (v2 + 0.32 / v1 + 0.55)))
    tmp = ((v1 * 0.96) * wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.41)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v0 + 0.85) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.65)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.02)
    v0 = (v0 + 0.43)
    tmp = v0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
